title: Mark Hildreth - Complex State Of Attachment (2008)
description:
This is the debut album of Mark Hildreth (commonly known as the voice actor of Heero Yuy from Gundam Wing).

I love this album; my favorite songs are Ready To Fall, Siddhartha, You In Me and I Just Wanna Love Someone, but then there's Beauty Of It All and It's My Life...! Such wonderful talent, I hope whomever tries enjoys! :D

128kbps, mp3

Tracklist
1. Magic Spell
2. Siddhartha
3. It's My Life
4. Ready To Fall
5. Love Will Make It Certain
6. Here I Am
7. Little Life
8. Beauty Of It All
9. You In Me
10. I Just Wanna Love Someone
